snippet.title: Domiverse - How to play - Shluuuups
snippet.description:
How to play Shluuuups

Son of the King Shluuups, the last winner of the Domiverse, the prince Shluuuups must win the crown to keep the domination of the universe.
Prince Shluuuups can load a ranged laser, but beware of the overload fart. To keep distance with the enemies, he drops paralysing mines.

http://domiverse.be

Steam store: http://store.steampowered.com/app/598880/Domiverse/
